author: stsp
msg: (svn_cl__add, svn_cl__changelist): When complaining about URLs where paths
are expected, use the SVN_ERR_CL_ARG_PARSING_ERROR error code instead of
SVN_ERR_ILLEGAL_TARGET. This causes an additional line to be printed
asking the user to try 'svn help' for more information. Of course,
we won't use this error code in the client library, just in the CLI client.
